I paid using Apple Pay which is super quick and convenient. This location is also a Baskin Robbins and sells ice cream cakes, which is good to know for future celebrations.

After 2-3 visit to DD this beatiful girl remember my order and had it ready for me before i even could make the order. Another day she even gave me a surprised flavor which really boosted my day. The service is beyond anything i ever seen in any DD chain resturant. Its became my priority to go every morning, they can literraly help start your day with a great smile.

I went here with an open mind, and should have left with an empty bag. The clerk made me repeat my order so many times I felt like saying, "Okay, just bring me WHATEVER YOU WANT." Being a Williamsburger I'd pretty much assumed everybody and his Shiba Inu can make a decent cafe latte but I have never been more wrong. Less than a dollar cheaper than Variety down the street but as different as an eggplant from a Ferrari. Save your taste buds and don't even THINK about it.
